{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act21side_level_act21side_04_end","storyGroup":"act21side","storySort":9,"storyDependence":"act21side_level_act21side_04_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"IS-4","storyName":"苦夜惊雷","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"一辆卡车冲入了法庭，对德克萨斯的审判被迫中止。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act21side/level_act21side_04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act21side_04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":7,"next":9,"characters":["收音机","空","能天使","可颂","女演员","拉维妮娅","好奇的看客","聒噪的看客","？？？","德克萨斯","刻薄的陪审团成员","多疑的陪审团成员","德米特里","莱昂图索","拉普兰德","甘比诺","卡彭","文"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/00/Avg_bg_33_g4_srctheater.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_newhope01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"text","text":"对她来说，她的生活方式是始终如一的，只是别人会因此说——","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"她像个叙拉古人。","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"她像叙拉古人吗？","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"她不知道。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"她只记得自己有一次和爷爷说过——","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"“我觉得，那些认为叙拉古的生活更加高贵的人，和认为哥伦比亚的生活更加高贵的人，都很无聊。”","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"爷爷哈哈大笑。","id":14},{"type":"dialog","id":15},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"今天，备受瞩目的卡拉奇部长遇刺案件即将开庭。","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"不过，似乎是出于安全考量，只有少数被邀请者能够进入法庭现场旁听。","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"其他人只能在法院外围等待审判的结果。","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"现在，法院已经被护卫重重包围，但是，依然有许多市民聚集在这里。","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"看来，卡拉奇部长的死还是牵动了许多市民的心。","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"我们会持续追踪报道，请听众们耐心等待。","id":23},{"type":"dialog","id":24},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_684_1#8$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":25},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"......","id":27,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_684_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#1$1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"空，准备好了吗？","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_684_1#1$1","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"嗯。","id":31,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/80/Avg_avg_npc_684_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"我在演出的时候，你们两个想去的话就去吧。","id":32,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/80/Avg_avg_npc_684_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#9$1","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"反正去了也进不去，还是算啦。","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/68/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_201_moeshd_1#13$1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可颂","text":"嗯，现在我们也只能耐心等待结果了。","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/54/Avg_avg_201_moeshd_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#10$1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"你在舞台上可要加油哦。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_684_1#9$1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"放心吧，我已经做好心理准备了。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/93/Avg_avg_npc_684_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":41},{"type":"character","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"女演员","text":"空，准备好了吗？要报幕了。","id":43},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_684_1#9$1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"来了！","id":45,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/93/Avg_avg_npc_684_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":46},{"type":"dialog","id":47},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":48},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":49},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":50},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_bg_33_g3_srccourt.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":51},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":52,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":53},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside","channel":"a","loop":"true","volume":"0.3","id":54},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":55},{"type":"text","text":"沃尔西尼法院","id":56},{"type":"dialog","id":57},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":58},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":59},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"安静，安静。","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"今天这场庭审，结果将对所有沃尔西尼的市民公开。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"今天审理的案件，是建设部部长卡拉奇遇刺一案。","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"将犯罪嫌疑人带上来。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":65},{"type":"character","id":66},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":67},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":68},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":70},{"type":"character","id":71},{"type":"musicvolume","channel":"a","volume":"0.5","fadetime":"2","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好奇的看客","text":"那就是......德克萨斯？","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"聒噪的看客","text":"那个发色和瞳色，不会有错！德克萨斯家的人！","id":74},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_692_1#3$1","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_692_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"Zzz......","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_692_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好奇的看客","text":"她怎么会还活着？","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"聒噪的看客","text":"她杀了卡拉奇？","id":80},{"type":"dialog","id":81},{"type":"playsound","key":"$gavel1","volume":"0.7","id":82},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#7$1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"肃静！","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d0/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"......","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d0/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"......","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"切利尼娜·德克萨斯，你曾出现在卡拉奇部长的遇害现场。","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"是的。","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"我安装了炸弹，在建设部部长路过的时候引爆了。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"好奇的看客","text":"她就这么承认了？！","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"聒噪的看客","text":"最后的德克萨斯......怎么如此堕落！","id":97},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"......你的动机是什么？","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"没有动机。","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"谁指使你的？","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"无人指使。","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"所以说，你独自做了这一切？","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"嗯。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":110},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"刻薄的陪审团成员","text":"不可能！你从哪里搞到的炸弹？又怎么可能有机会安装呢！","id":112},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"这重要吗？","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多疑的陪审团成员","text":"你是不是来为德克萨斯家族复仇的？","id":116},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"不是。","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多疑的陪审团成员","text":"可是......","id":120},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"拉维妮娅法官，我已经供认了一切。","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"这几位坐在陪审团席位上的家族成员也实在太吵了一点。","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"刻薄的陪审团成员","text":"你！","id":125},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#2$1","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"这些多余的流程，我们是不是可以干脆跳过？","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7a/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":128},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":130},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":131},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/74/Avg_bg_33_g11_mansionhall.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":132},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":133},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":134},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":135},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","fadetime":"1","id":136},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":137},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#5$1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"嗯？","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d8/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"莱昂，你怎么还在这？","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d8/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我还以为，你会在法庭。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d8/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"你真的意外吗，德米特？","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"......要喝点什么吗？","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"早上的话，我建议不要喝酒，我来给你调一些提神的果汁。","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"威士忌，最烈的。","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/77/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"然后，回答我的问题。","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"你是怎么猜到的？","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"很简单啊。","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"对我的袭击也好，对卡拉奇的刺杀也好，都说明，有人想要十二家族互相猜忌。","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"而且，拉维妮娅作为贝洛内在这件事上的代言人，一定要无法找到凶手，否则的话，事态也会得到一定控制。","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"所以，在拉维妮娅逮捕切利尼娜后，对方一定不希望这场庭审进行。","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"那么，拉维妮娅会遇上什么呢？","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"还好，你没有成功。","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"你自己可能没有察觉，但她已经给你带去了许多影响。","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"这让你的行为开始愈发摇摆。","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"而通过对你的影响，拉维妮娅自己可能也开始相信，自己是能做到一些什么的。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我必须掐断这种不切实际的妄想。","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"......真亏你能理直气壮地说出这样的话。","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"不，莱昂。","id":170,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我并不是心安理得做这些事的。","id":172,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我不希望等到一切结束的时候告诉你结果，让你被迫接受。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"所以，你说得对，还好我没有成功。","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"但你还是做了。","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"这笔账，我们可以慢慢算。","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"说回来，切利尼娜在庭审前夕离奇死亡显然更安全，但什么都没发生。","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"这说明——对方忌惮着切利尼娜的身份。","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"毕竟，且不说她是最后的德克萨斯，她也是老头子带回来的人。","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"也就是说，只有家族里的人会甘心放过这个机会。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"而昨天，切利尼娜确实没有受到任何袭击。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"如果对方猜到了这是你设下的陷阱而故意没有出手呢？","id":185,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"如果对方下定决心挑战西西里夫人的权威，那么，动静想必不小，我也只需要查一查哪一家这两天动作比较大就好。","id":187,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"而事实是，你，德米特里，在推动这一切。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"......","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"不得不说，切利尼娜小姐会主动接受审判确实在我的意料之外。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"原以为她有没有被卷进来对计划不会有什么影响，现在看来，我确实应该把她的存在考虑在内。","id":192,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"......你也不用妄自菲薄，如果不是切利尼娜主动说她愿意背上这个罪名，对我来说，这么做也是下策。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"这么说的话，你应该感谢她。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"我当然会感谢她。但是在那之前，我只想知道，德米特，为什么？","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"这不是显而易见的事吗，我是家族的叛徒。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"我可以相信所有人是叛徒，但唯独你，我不会相信。","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"如果我不能相信你，那我还能相信谁？","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"......","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"莱昂，你怎么看待这座新的移动城市？","id":206,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"......当然是新的利益分配。","id":208,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"谁能笑到最后，谁就是最大的赢家。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"你说得很对，但在我看来，这里是西西里夫人的一块试验田。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"借着建造新城市的名头，让十二个家族在这里竞争。","id":212,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"新生代的狼崽子们可以在这里宣泄被压抑的血性，狡猾的老狼们也可以有一个新的目标。","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"多好，哥伦比亚家族的回归，一下子就把叙拉古这一潭死水给盘活了。","id":214,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"无论谁最后胜利，对于高坐在灰厅之上的西西里夫人来说，都不是坏事。","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"你......难道说......","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/cd/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"这些年你做得很好，不仅压制了大部分其他家族，也确实牢牢掌握住了建设部。","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"这样发展下去，贝洛内确实能够笑到最后。","id":220,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"但是，那又怎么样呢？","id":222,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我们的家族在一座新的移动城市中获得了绝对的掌控力，然后，一切照常进行。","id":223,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"......你不甘心，不，是他不甘心对吗？","id":225,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"自灰厅建立以来，自十二家族之间不得互相倾轧的规则建立以来，哪个家族甘心过？","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我们曾经是无所顾忌的狼，百年前的家族斗争曾经不死不休。","id":228,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"然而，新生代的狼崽子甚至已经习惯了枷锁的存在。","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"习惯了和其他家族共存，习惯了冲突之后寻找和平的解决方法，习惯了在灰厅中和其他家族争执所谓的利益分配。","id":230,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我们本来没有这么做的必要。","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":232},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"所以，他想要推翻灰厅！怎么可能？","id":234,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/cd/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"那一位允许各个家族各自为政，但她决不允许有家族违背她定下的规矩——家族之间不能有明面上的斗争。","id":236,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我们即将取得胜利，也只有在这个前提下，我们的突然失势才能够引起所有家族的觊觎。","id":238,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"斗争是狼的天性，只要让他们闻到血腥味，再温驯的狼也会按捺不住。","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"他们会互相撕咬的。","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"只有这样，那位才会走出灰厅。","id":241,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"而我们等的，就是那个时候。","id":243,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#3$1","focus":"1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"......","id":245,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/59/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":246},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bottlebroken","volume":"0.8","id":247},{"type":"text","text":"“喀”，清脆的玻璃碎裂声在安静的房间中响起。","id":248},{"type":"text","text":"而幼狼对被碎片划破的伤口浑然未觉。","id":249},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我们会笑到最后，莱昂。","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"到那时候，我们获得的不是一座新的移动城市，而是整个叙拉古。","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"这就是你的父亲，一手将贝洛内打造成十二家族中最为强盛的家族之人——贝纳尔多·贝洛内想要做的事。","id":253,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"......","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"不对。","id":256,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"嗯？","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"我没有拦住你，不，你还有后手，是吗？","id":260,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"从一开始，你就知道自己的行动会暴露，所以你是故意在这里等我的。","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我在这里，是因为我觉得，我有必要面对你的怒火。","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我应当向你请罪，无论是身为挚友，还是身为你的手下。","id":264,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我做的事无法被原谅，但我至少不希望被你认为，我是心安理得地做下这些事。","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":266},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"少在这里发表像是胜利者一样的宣言！","id":268,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/48/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"......我输了，真的，莱昂。","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"但或许是叙拉古就是这样的地方，又或许是，首领的野心是正确的。","id":271,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"在我就要承认自己的失败时，她出现了。","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/52/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"她？","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/cd/Avg_avg_427_vigil_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"一个疯子。","id":276,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":277},{"type":"dialog","id":278},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":279},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":280},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":281},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_bg_33_g5_srcpark.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":282},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":283},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkalley_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_longmendarkalley_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":284,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":285},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#9$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":286},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"甘比诺，你能想象到的，让一个人最痛苦的方法是什么？","id":288,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_542_1#1$1","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"甘比诺","text":"啊？把一个人的脖子砍到一半吧。","id":290,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_542_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#9$1","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"你呢，卡彭？","id":292,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_541_1#1$1","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡彭","text":"找到他的亲朋好友，然后一个一个地做掉，再把照片给他看。","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_541_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#9$1","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"唉，所以我说，你们永远成不了气候。","id":296,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_542_1#1$1","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"甘比诺","text":"哈，你又能有什么高招？","id":298,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_542_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"信念，朋友，信念。","id":300,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_541_1#1$1","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡彭","text":"毁了他的信念？","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_541_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"毁了？不，你怎么能去亲手毁了别人的信念，你做不到的。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"你要做的是轻轻一推，让他目睹自己的信念从空中落下。","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"multiline","name":"拉普兰德","text":"然后，咻——","id":306},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"15","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":307},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#5$1","id":308},{"type":"multiline","name":"拉普兰德","text":"砰！","id":309},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"摔个粉碎。","id":311,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_541_1#1$1","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡彭","text":"一个人的信念哪有那么容易自己摔碎。","id":313,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_541_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#9$1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"不不不，你不明白，信念是高洁的，而我们的生活却是污浊的。","id":315,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"“哪有那么容易”？","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"实际上，哪有那么困难？","id":318,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_541_1#1$1","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡彭","text":"所以......这就是你让我们准备一辆卡车的理由？","id":320,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_541_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_542_1#1$1","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"甘比诺","text":"哈，我懂了，所以你要去撞死那个法官，好让德克萨斯动摇，对吧。","id":322,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a8/Avg_avg_npc_542_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#9$1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"她像是会单纯地因为一个人的死而崩溃的人吗？","id":324,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_541_1#1$1","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡彭","text":"那你要干什么？","id":326,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_541_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":327},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":328},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":329},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":330},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_bar_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":331},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":332},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#5$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":334},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"被萨卢佐除名的拉普兰德，为什么你会在沃尔西尼？","id":336,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d8/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"不，你是如何回到叙拉古的？！","id":338,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#9$1","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"就好像，贝洛内和切利尼娜有谁也不知道的联系，我不得不承认，我和萨卢佐这个姓氏之间，也有一种令人作呕的联系。","id":340,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"......所以，你代表萨卢佐而来。","id":342,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#9$1","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"你可以这么认为。","id":344,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"我建议你把吧台下的武器收起来。","id":345,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"死在这里对你和你的计划没有任何帮助。","id":346,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"......","id":348,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#9$1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"来做个交易吧，贝洛内的狼崽。","id":350,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"你不是想要庭审中止吗？","id":351,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"我来帮你。","id":352,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#7$1","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"这是......阿尔贝托·萨卢佐的意思？","id":354,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"我是他的女儿，我比任何人都了解他。","id":356,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":357},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":359},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":360},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_bg_33_g5_srcpark.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":361},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":362},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#9$1","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"你们不是一直很好奇我回到叙拉古到底想做什么吗？","id":365,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"我想做的事情很简单，我要让她明白......","id":366,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"叙拉古是一座泥潭，谁都别想轻易逃出去。","id":367,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#1$1","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"谁都别想。","id":369,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b7/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":370},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":371},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":372},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":373},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fe/Avg_bg_33_g3_srccourt.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":374},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":376},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"因此，你对上述行为供认不讳。","id":378,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"是的。","id":380,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":381},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","id":382},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"在此，我宣布，切利尼娜·德克萨斯谋杀建设部部长卡拉奇的罪名成立。","id":384,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#2$1","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"判决为——","id":386,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ee/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":387},{"type":"playsound","key":"$sportscarstart","volume":"0.2","id":388},{"type":"dialog","id":389},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":390},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside","channel":"a","loop":"true","volume":"0.4","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"刻薄的陪审团成员","text":"怎么了？","id":392},{"type":"playsound","key":"$sportscarstart","volume":"0.2","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多疑的陪审团成员","text":"你没有听到什么声音吗？","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"刻薄的陪审团成员","text":"......这是，引擎的声音？","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多疑的陪审团成员","text":"这里可是法院，怎么会——","id":396},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":397},{"type":"text","text":"于曾经的家族们来说，心照不宣的规则高于一切。","id":398},{"type":"text","text":"西西里夫人却将名为律法的枷锁套在了家族的脖子上。","id":399},{"type":"text","text":"于是，每座叙拉古城市中都有一座法院。","id":400},{"type":"text","text":"在叙拉古，法院的存在，代表着灰厅的意志。","id":401},{"type":"text","text":"而法官，更是西西里夫人意志的代行者。","id":402},{"type":"text","text":"法官往往不可避免地受制于家族，甚至臣服于家族，然而，每个法官都知道，他们有一条不可忘却的底线——","id":403},{"type":"text","text":"监视并预防十二家族之间的斗争。","id":404},{"type":"text","text":"正如十二家族也都知道，他们的一举一动，总是在西西里夫人的监视之下。","id":405},{"type":"text","text":"于是，一种微妙的平衡，通过法院的存在被建立了。","id":406},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":407},{"type":"text","text":"然而——","id":408},{"type":"dialog","id":409},{"type":"playsound","key":"$smallearthquake","id":410},{"type":"playsound","key":"$sportscarstart","id":411},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_explosion_stone","delay":"0.3","id":412},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":413},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"4","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"40","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":414},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_33_i03.png","xScale":"1.3","yScale":"1.3","x":"200","y":"100","fadetime":"0","id":415},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":416},{"type":"imagetween","xTo":"100","yTo":"0","duration":"2","block":"false","id":417},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rockfall","id":418},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_33_i03.png","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","x":"100","y":"0","fadetime":"2","id":419},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_collapse","id":420},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_truckengine","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":421},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleTo":"1.1","yScaleTo":"1.1","duration":"30","block":"false","id":422},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"-1","xstrength":"3","ystrength":"1","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","block":"false","id":423},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$tense_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_tense_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":424,"musicid":3},{"type":"text","text":"像是在宣告着对西西里夫人的藐视。","id":425},{"type":"text","text":"像是在嘲笑着叙拉古的法律本身。","id":426},{"type":"text","text":"伴随着轰鸣的引擎声，以及夹在其中的高笑声。","id":427},{"type":"text","text":"一辆卡车破壁而入。","id":428},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/db/Avg_33_i03.png","xScale":"0.88","yScale":"0.88","x":"50","fadetime":"2","id":429},{"type":"imagetween","xTo":"-50","duration":"30","block":"false","id":430},{"type":"text","text":"并且，即使在冲进来后，它的引擎也没有停止下来。","id":431},{"type":"text","text":"像是在告诉其他人——","id":432},{"type":"text","text":"它并不是偶然为之，而是刻意如此。","id":433},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"2","xstrength":"3","ystrength":"1","vibrato":"40","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":434},{"type":"dialog","id":435},{"type":"image","fadetime":"1.5","id":436},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":437},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"刻薄的陪审团成员","text":"噫——","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"多疑的陪审团成员","text":"怎、怎么回事？！为什么会有卡车！","id":440},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#3$1","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"车上的人是谁！立刻下来！","id":442,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f8/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":443},{"type":"dialog","id":444},{"type":"character","id":445},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cardoorc","id":446},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":447},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":448},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","fadetime":"1","id":449},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"嗯，不错，是我想要看到的表情。","id":451,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#3$1","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"你是什么人？！","id":453,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f8/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"啊，日安，尊敬的女士们，先生们。","id":455,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"请允许我自我介绍一番。","id":456,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉普兰德","text":"我的名字是——拉普兰德·萨卢佐。","id":457,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_683_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#4$1","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"萨卢佐？！","id":459,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2b/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","id":460},{"type":"multiline","name":"拉普兰德","text":"同时也是，","id":461},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_683_1#3$1","id":462},{"type":"multiline","name":"拉普兰德","text":"刺杀卡拉奇的真凶。","id":463},{"type":"dialog","id":464},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":465},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":466},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":467},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f3/Avg_bg_33_g10_smallrestaurant.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":468},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":469},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":470},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","id":471},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"突发情况，突发情况！","id":472},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"就在刚才，有一辆卡车忽然冲入庭审现场。","id":473},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"而做出这样惊人之举的人，名叫拉普兰德·萨卢佐。","id":474},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"并且，她还自称是刺杀卡拉奇的真凶。","id":475},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"目前，拉维妮娅法官已经中止了本次庭审，并将其逮捕。","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"收音机","text":"我们会继续追踪后续的发展，请关注——","id":477},{"type":"dialog","id":478},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_694_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":479},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文","text":"当所有人都不再将血腥味认为是血腥味时，血腥也就成了文明的一部分。","id":481,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_694_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文","text":"一次漂亮的警醒。","id":482,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_694_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文","text":"在这座连下水道都已经满溢着阴谋和血腥的城市里，还能发生这样的趣事。","id":483,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_694_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_694_1#5$1","id":484},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文","text":"天生向往荒野的狼，你果然能为人带来惊喜。","id":485,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_694_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文","text":"但你又是否能挣脱自己的枷锁呢？我很期待。","id":486,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0f/Avg_avg_npc_694_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":487},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":488},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":489},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":490},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_bg_33_g5_srcpark.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":491},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_031","name2":"avg_npc_031","id":492},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":493},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":494},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","id":495},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_031","fadetime":"0.5","id":496},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":497},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","id":498},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":499},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":500},{"type":"text","text":"十数个家族成员躺在地上哀嚎。","id":501},{"type":"text","text":"场上唯一站立着的，是一名拿着长弓的少女。","id":502},{"type":"dialog","id":503},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4014_lunacu_1#8$2","fadetime":"1","id":504},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":505},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"城市里的狼，原来这么软弱。","id":506,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/00/Avg_avg_4014_lunacu_1-8$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"阿涅塞说得对。","id":507,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/00/Avg_avg_4014_lunacu_1-8$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4014_lunacu_1#9$2","id":508},{"type":"text","text":"她顿了顿，忽然，向某个方向嗅了嗅。","id":509},{"type":"text","text":"那是法院的方向。","id":510},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4014_lunacu_1#1$2","id":511},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这座城市里还有别的来自荒野的狼？","id":512,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/35/Avg_avg_4014_lunacu_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4014_lunacu_1#2$2","id":513},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......不，这不是荒野的味道。","id":514,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/96/Avg_avg_4014_lunacu_1-2$2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4014_lunacu_1#1$2","id":515},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"但是，很像。","id":516,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/35/Avg_avg_4014_lunacu_1-1$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":517},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":518},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":519},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":520},{"type":"character","id":521},{"type":"image","id":522}],"characters":["收音机","空","能天使","可颂","女演员","拉维妮娅","好奇的看客","聒噪的看客","？？？","德克萨斯","刻薄的陪审团成员","多疑的陪审团成员","德米特里","莱昂图索","拉普兰德","甘比诺","卡彭","文"]}